videos.description: Colorado strikes first as Steven Montez throws a dime to K.D. Nixon for a 32-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Colorado's Montez finds WR for 32-yard TD

videos.description: Jack Colletto's pass is tipped up and picked off by Dante Wigley, who takes it back 27 yards for a Colorado touchdown.
videos.headline: Colorado's Wigley takes pick back for TD

videos.description: Travon Mcmillian dashes through the middle of the Oregon State defense for a 75-yard Colorado touchdown.
videos.headline: Colorado's McMillian gallops in for 75-yard TD

videos.description: Steven Montez threads the needle to K.D. Nixon who makes a one-handed snag between two Beaver defenders for a 39-yard gain.
videos.headline: Colorado WR makes one-handed catch between two defenders

videos.description: Oregon State rallies back to tie the game as Jake Luton finds Trevon Bradford for 10-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Beavers' Luton throws 10-yard TD to tie game
